snippet: Lisa Moore’s lucid, committed pianism made the best of four works, each dealing with an aspect of landscape or nature.
abstract: David Allen reviews Kettle Corn New Music concert of contemporary music based on landscape or nature theme, performed by Lisa Moore, at DiMenna Center.
lead_paragraph: Lisa Moore’s lucid, committed pianism made the best of four works, each dealing with an aspect of landscape or nature.

headline.main: Review: Lisa Moore at DiMenna Center
